About Mercantile Bank Corp.
501-1000 EmployeesBased in Grand Rapids, Michigan

Visit website


Mercantile Bank Corporation operates as the holding company for Mercantile Bank of Michigan that provides commercial and retail banking products and services primarily to small-to medium-sized businesses and individuals. 
Ticker:MBWMExchange:NASDAQ (See More NASDAQ Companies)Industry:Regional - Midwest Banks (See More Regional - Midwest Banks Companies)Sector:Financial (See More Financial Companies)


